      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Held Peter and John, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " in an ecstasy of thankfulness unto them, they having been the instruments of so great a mercy from God towards him; as also out of fear, lest when they were gone he might relapse: he that found so great a change in himself could not but be as much surprised as they that saw the change upon him. ",
        "children": []
